result.name: dmag-briefings-2006
result.notes:
An archive of Briefings and Updates published in 2006 by the GLA's Data Management and Analysis Group.

These Briefings cover a range of topics including demography, census analysis, education, and London's labour market.

Briefings from other years are available here: [DMAG Report Archive – London Datastore](https://data.london.gov.uk/demography/dmag-report-archive/)
